fields.query_expression: with finwire_unmatches as (select count(*) umatched_counts from $project.$dataset.$table f1 where industryID not in (select in_id from reference.Industry)), finwire_total as (select count(*) as total_counts from $project.$dataset.$table) select round((total_counts - umatched_counts) / total_counts * 100) as degree from finwire_unmatches, finwire_total
